{"text_id":24009,"tokens":["Title",":"," Inside","-","Out"," Ev","acuation"," of"," Transitional"," Pro","top","lan","etary"," Dis","ks"," by"," the"," Magneto","-","Rot","ational"," Instability","\n\n","Abstract",":"," In"," this"," study",","," we"," investigate"," the"," role"," of"," the"," magneto","-","rot","ational"," instability"," (","MRI",")"," in"," the"," inside","-","out"," evacuation"," of"," transitional"," pro","top","lan","etary"," disks","."," Transitional"," disks",","," characterized"," by"," their"," central"," cavities",","," pose"," significant"," challenges"," to"," our"," understanding"," of"," disk"," evolution"," and"," planet"," formation","."," We"," aim"," to"," elucidate"," the"," mechanisms"," driving"," the"," formation"," of"," these"," cavities",","," focusing"," on"," the"," MRI"," as"," a"," potential"," catalyst","."," Our"," motivation"," stems"," from"," the"," need"," to"," reconcile"," observational"," data"," with"," theoretical"," models",","," thereby"," enhancing"," our"," comprehension"," of"," disk"," dynamics"," and"," the"," early"," stages"," of"," planetary"," system"," development","."," Utilizing"," advanced"," magneto","hydro","dynamic"," simulations",","," we"," examine"," the"," conditions"," under"," which"," MRI"," can"," induce"," substantial"," mass"," transport"," and"," disk"," evacuation","."," Our"," results"," demonstrate"," that"," MRI"," can"," indeed"," generate"," sufficient"," turbulence"," and"," angular"," momentum"," transfer"," to"," facilitate"," the"," formation"," of"," central"," cavities","."," We"," find"," that"," the"," efficiency"," of"," this"," process"," is"," highly"," sensitive"," to"," the"," disk","'","s"," ionization"," state"," and"," magnetic"," field"," strength","."," These"," findings"," provide"," critical"," insights"," into"," the"," physical"," processes"," governing"," transitional"," disks"," and"," offer"," a"," plausible"," explanation"," for"," their"," observed"," structures","."," Our"," work"," underscores"," the"," importance"," of"," magnetic"," effects"," in"," disk"," evolution"," and"," sets"," the"," stage"," for"," future"," observational"," and"," theoretical"," investigations"," into"," the"," complex"," interplay"," between"," magnetic"," fields"," and"," disk"," dynamics","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt4o","label":1}